title: Introducing ‘Body Bags’! Episode 1: Death in the Tetons
itunes:title: Introducing ‘Body Bags’! Episode 1: Death in the Tetons
description:
Introducing the new podcast 'Body Bags with Joseph Scott Morgan'!

Gabby Petito went missing during a cross-country road trip with her boyfriend, Brian Laundrie. On Sept. 19, the FBI announced that a body had been found in Wyoming. An autopsy confirmed the remains belonged to Petito. Her cause of death has not been revealed yet, but it has been ruled a homicide. Death investigator Joseph Scott Morgan weighs in on why the cause of death has not been revealed.
